---
import VizPlaceholder from '../VizPlaceholder.astro';

const components = [
  {
    name: 'Loop',
    body: 'Run the model, act, feed results back, repeat until done.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Tool interface',
    body: 'How the agent reads files, runs commands, and calls MCP servers.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Context management',
    body: 'What goes into the window, and what gets evicted.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Control',
    body: 'Permissions, approvals, and guardrails on what the agent may do.',
  },
];
---

<section id="harness" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-accent">
      The base
    </p>
    <h2
      class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-50 sm:text-4xl"
    >
      What is a harness
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-xl font-medium text-neutral-200">
      A harness is the runtime that turns a model into an agent.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-300">
      <p>
        The model predicts tokens. The harness is everything around it that
        turns prediction into action. It's often described as having four
        components.
      </p>
    </div>

    <dl class="mt-8 grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-800 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {
        components.map((c) => (
          <div class="bg-neutral-950 p-6">
            <dt class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-100">{c.name}</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
              {c.body}
            </dd>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </dl>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-300">
      Claude Code, Codex, and OpenCode are harnesses.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="mt-8 border-l border-neutral-700 pl-5 text-lg italic leading-relaxed text-neutral-400"
    >
      The model is the engine. The harness is the chassis, wheels, and steering.
      The agent is the car that actually goes somewhere.
    </blockquote>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-5xl">
    <VizPlaceholder label="step-build diagram, an LLM tile with four component tiles snapping in to form an agent" />
  </div>
</section>
